<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٦٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4670">عُمَرُ بْنُ حَفْصٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1556">أَبِي: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6121">مُسْلِمٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6088">مَسْرُوقٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«خَيَّرَنَا رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَاخْتَرْنَا اللهَ وَرَسُولَهُ، فَلَمْ يَعُدَّ ذَلِكَ عَلَيْنَا شَيْئًا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>